{"word":"βαρύστονος","slug":"βαρύστονος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>βαρύστονος</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:στένω'><el>στένω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>groaning heavily, bellowing</i>, <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b>:—<a href='S:Adverb'>adv.</a> <el>-νως</el>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b>of things, <i>heavily lamented, grievous</i>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}